				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi!
<br />

<br />
Something is not normal with my Bard:
<br />
I have a Level 25 Bard (Half Elf).
<br />
She is a little bit twinked... <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
1. At Level 17 i bought a new weapon (1H Slashing) and i make up to 35 Dmg with it (at Level 17!). Is there no DMG-Cap at Level 17?
<br />

<br />
2. I use my AE-Spells to Kite in Lake of ill Omen. I thought i can only hit 4 Mobs with my AE-Spells... But it seems to be all i pull... I pull 10 Mobs out of the fort, and they all go down at the same time (not the same time, but near by). At the messages in my Chatwindow says, that more the 4 Mobs get DMG from my AE-Spells...
<br />

<br />
3. At Level 14 i get the Skill &quot;Wind-Instruments&quot;. The list of this website says, that i have to &quot;train&quot; it (at a Bard-GM) befor i can use it. But i dont have to do that! Same with Dual Wield! I get the skill &quot;automaticly&quot;!
<br />

<br />
Ok, thats all good for me, but is that normal?
<br />

<br />
Thanks for Information!
<br />
Rahya</span></td>
